Check whether Leadbay has a pending clarification question — a question raised when refining the intelligence prompt produced contradictory or ambiguous criteria. Returns `{pending: false, clarification: null}` when nothing is pending (the backend returns 204).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after leadbay_refine_prompt, to see if Leadbay needs the user to disambiguate.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} to answer the question — use leadbay_answer_clarification.
